## MODULES/HDeskExt/Hdesk: hDesk.sys

SetEnv CORE_DIR $[HOME]/.fvwm/coreEXT/
SetEnv HOME_DIR $[HOME]/.fvwm

## Close Modules
KillModule FvwmButtons Bg*
KillModule FvwmButtons Grid*
KillModule FvwmButtons *RightPanel
KillModule FvwmButtons FvwmOverView
KillModule FvwmButtons ControlPanelB
KillModule FvwmButtons ExitPanel
KillModule FvwmButtons WinListB
KillModule FvwmButtons HDesk

## Load pages grid lines.
Read $[CORE_DIR]/MODULES/HDeskExt/Hdesk/gridPageFunc.sys

Read $[CORE_DIR]/MODULES/HDeskExt/Hdesk/horizontalDesk.sys

## Change pre-settings of FvwmOverView
Read $[EXTRA_DIR]/MODULES/FvwmOverView/fvwmWOview.sys
*FvwmOverView: Geometry 77x36+8+20

KillModule FvwmButtons SimpleButton
Read $[CORE_DIR]/MODULES/SimpleButton/simpleB.sys
*SimpleButton: Geometry 350x40-530+20

## Change Maximize
Mouse 1 4 A Maximize 160 100

### Thumbnail
## Minimize to Thumbnail Placeholder
Style * IconBox 400x600+20+50, IconGrid 1 1, \
IconFill top left, !IconTitle, IconBackgroundRelief 0

AddToFunc Thumbnail
+ I Stick
